Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone in the Earth. This is the spaceship Titanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been ten days since we departed from the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon Tour with 450 passengers is very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are traveling through the course very smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nishiyama from Aurora firm, how does it feel like to be aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the drinks! The most expensive one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:02:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This couple is the happiest one that won the raffle of 500,000 couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the space honeymoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The designer of this space passenger ship, Doctor Kanda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Minister of Science Doctor Ochanomizu are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-How comfortable, Doctor. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all thanks to my teacher, Doctor Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Meteor is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone in the Earth, please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest automatic barrier device of this Titan ship
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,will bounce this meteor off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, computer's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shift it to manual operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't work, Captain! It's too late to shift now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fool Ivan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Announcement to passengers. Titan ship will soon explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get on the assigned life-ship and evacuate to Lagrande's satellite base!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Kanda! Where did Dr. Ochanomizu go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the life-ship with the crowd. He will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough life-ships. Can we do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be extra life-ship beside the engine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh. -Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hurry, Atom! -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank God. -Ah... It was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The rudder instrument is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to reach Lagrande's evacuation base like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we not survive somehow, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We are willing to pay as much as you want. Isn't there any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We can reach the Moon if we keep traveling like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get off at the Moon and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do there? There isn't atmosphere anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside temperature is -200℃.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- -200℃? -It feels like I'm freezing just to hear the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's shoot a rocket and ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon base camp might sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange. It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work no matter how hard I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's over now. We are all going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is that? -Huh? Is there something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm scared, honey. -It might be alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check the situation, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Be careful, Atom. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster! I'll figure out who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's a dead tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ice. Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-All right. That's air. -Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Air must have frozen for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have arrived at a crater with atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Do you want me to bring that ice into the life-ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't work. Since this rocket has some heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it melts when it gets closer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, there is the list of people who's gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Kanda and Atom, and Nishiyama Narika,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarui Hutoshi, the executive of a company,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,TV announcer, newly-weds, and a 14-year-old boy. Total of eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we are sending out communication wave
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,around 100,000km radius of the explosion spot, but there's no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, even if they did escape with the life-ship, they must be out of air by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be alive. Atom, Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot. It feels like I'm in sauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's hard to breathe. -I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We will be out of air within an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then! Then we will be suffocated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Honey! -Ah, Noriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffocate? Gosh! That's not possible! Are you telling me to die in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? Please do something. Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Air in this life-ship is all mine. There's none for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's a pistol. -How did you get such...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know. Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama. You used to be in a gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that kind of threat here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon's dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Frozen air is starting to melt. It's vaporizing with solar heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We are safe! According to this gas analyzer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the amount of oxygen in this air is almost the same as the Earth's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey! We are safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Us too. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's colder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but I can bear this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold air tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How impressive! How could I express this feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is it? -Ah, it's grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's amazing. It really grows fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A day at the Moon is the same as four weeks in the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Plants grow within that hour
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and when the night falls, it becomes -200℃and everything dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the night falls and air freezes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to fix the broken part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-It looks like a male human. -I'll go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster's that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very old looking rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an old cassette player.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Minya Mikhailovna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying officer of the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Female voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I safely arrived at the surface of the Moon with the probe rocket Ural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it fell from a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rocket fell into a deep crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was safe fortunately, but the rocket was heavily damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the communication device was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to die. And that was the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw some air bursting like smoke along with dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I jumped out and started shedding tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, my life as Robinson Crusoe began.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ivan the robot does the tough works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ivan is the first human-like robot of the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I acquired underground water with the help of Ivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I pumped air to the rocket and saved it as liquid oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could survive somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Ivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go back to the Earth! To the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I discovered something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not worth anything in this Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave that diamond as earrings to Ivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My body weakened day by day. I got disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then today, I felt that my day is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ivan, we will soon part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last order. If I die, bury me in that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If a person comes here later, the diamond valley...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How poor. How lonely must that one had been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ivan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Atom. I heard your story. How lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mistake me for Minya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a robot like you. So get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You are glad to see a person after a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are wrong for suggesting such trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have married you if this were to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There are fruits! Fruits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Fruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disgusting color.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Toxic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-You try first. -Why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious. This one's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there. There are tons over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... A rocket from 30 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let me tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then! Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? 30 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And that pilot survived after such an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We gave up a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, efforts won't pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When the night falls, everything freezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too soon to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to discover new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot also discovered the valley of diamonds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Di!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mond!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What about diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to dogs or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's not worth anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Odd... It should be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Doctor! -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wow! -Yay! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a response to our communication wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the Moon! There was a response from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ochanomizu! Ochanomizu, is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Rescue rocket is on its way to the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? Really? -Is the rocket coming for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We fixed the buoy, so we were able to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be here by this evening at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Safe. -We are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You said there were diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Where is the valley of diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know of two that became Ivan's earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where is that robot, Atom? -No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those diamonds are Ivan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please, Atom. -No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all be rich. Please, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us, Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to take Ivan's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Move away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Atom. Guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't this one's chest will melt in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is an old robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that one called Ivan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom! Go tell him to give us diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Move quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ivan, where are your diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamonds. Those shiny things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Those you used to wear here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, what is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He buried those diamonds with Minya's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, dig it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ivan buried them with sincerity. -Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Dig, dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is a grave. I don't want to rob a grave! -Dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't dig.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How sad would it be for Ivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's suddenly cold. -Here! Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be dangerous if we don't go back quickly. We will freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have enough time until sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? It will be late if we don't go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Go back when diamonds are in front of my eyes? You go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yoshio, hold onto my legs. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be in such flurry. We have enough time to dig and go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, two egg-sized diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I could buy anything with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You! What are you trying to do with me? Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me go! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun will set if I act so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunset. Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, help me! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A big earthquake is coming to Shimoda town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was a lie of the robot called Thor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird. Robots can't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thor looks after Kozue, who has problems with eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This time, a big earthquake for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Robot Who Lied." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "The Robot Who Lied"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.07,0:23:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:24:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
